item.title: AWS Glue Masking PII
item.description: This project will walkthorugh AWS Glue products, such as data catalog, databases, tables, crawlers, and glue jobs, resulting in sensitive data found within a csv file being masked with ‘****’

item.title: AWS Cloud Resume Challenge
item.description: The AWS Cloud Resume Challenge revolves around creating a serverless resume website that incorporates various AWS services. This challenge provision the infrastructure for the front-end, back-end and CI/CD pipeline.
